d":2336791,"uid":361936,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f25671e0963108424be65fc5a3ebf5dd2d649a2a","tid":2336791,"uid":367723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T23:41:06.000Z","msg":"結果呢個post無一個用過airpods max<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T02:16:10.000Z","msg":"我一早開咗自用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n免費<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，多謝apple/先達"},{"pid":"fd736497fb0c28129c724ce5984ff5c7c4418265","tid":2336791,"uid":51717,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T03:14:26.000Z","msg":"此POST盡顯IDOG護主，諉過於人嘅本性<br />\n<br />\n同某啲仆街政權乜都唔覺得自己有錯, 有乜撚分別?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"392bca38338d6802a5876e7b251d2463c18ecc9a","tid":2336791,"uid":28001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T04:38:00.000Z","msg":"on9 理論"},{"pid":"ebae2f8ce476fd49f061c4f0fff08b42bca45fc1","tid":2336791,"uid":194130,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"53c5d525aff2124a47a5f2215a6f8b191dd5b06e","tid":2336791,"uid":188593,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"80d926167246735bbe6ba4225d6030b197e7e816","tid":2336791,"uid":33904,"like":38,"dislike":3,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"bcf619bb6f4a06a247abc66bd2403cf8cc6d8a9d","tid":2336791,"uid":71441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T00:42:40.000Z","msg":"眼見Airpods max 咁貴，唔少人用佢同中高價耳牛比較，話低音失真，高音延展唔夠，樂器分離差，聲場窄。繼而指控Apple is dead，昆水魚，idog/炒狗死全家云云。<br />\n<br />\n理性啲講，差唔係因為apple固意偷工減料，而係因為佢俾電池重量呢個物理限制箍實。<br />\n<br />\n要將耳機粒單元推得好，除咗解碼（DAC ）同放大（preamp） 晶片都要用靚料，但最緊要係俾足夠嘅電去推。至於source，爭議好大，但數據話AAC 已經夠做，人耳blind test 分唔到佢同flac。統計學証明bitrate係心理作用大過實際。至於hi-res，dsd768 ，2千幾kbps ，200mb 一隻歌，係對真善美嘅追求，未必關音樂聆聽體驗事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔信自己試下：<a href=\"https://www.npr.org/sections/therecord/2015/06/02/411473508/how-well-can-you-hear-audio-quality\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2Fsections%2Ftherecord%2F2015%2F06%2F02%2F411473508%2Fhow-well-can-you-hear-audio-quality&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpKix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=2bd870af\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.npr.org/sections/therecord/2015/06/02/411473508/how-well-can-you-hear-audio-quality</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://abx.digitalfeed.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fabx.digitalfeed.net%2F&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpKix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=30519ddb\" target=\"_blank\">http://abx.digitalfeed.net/</a><br />\n<br />\n不過新出嘅MQA有啲意思，因為代表studio直出，唔會經串流平台自己再壓縮，轉bitrate，令聽嘅人個心安樂啲，唔再驚失真。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於咩為之足料呢，舉個例，fiio q5s（1手$3200, 2手賣緊$1500）,  雙AK4493eq DAC+ thx aaa preamp，藍芽支援ldac。三頻，解析力，樂器分離，聲場照顧周到。三粒主要晶片，3800mAh 嘅電推到9個鐘。<br />\n<br />\nAirpods max 用唔夠1000mAh 都要做齊呢三樣嘢，再加消噪，仲要行20hr ，音質就每一part都打個超大嘅折扣。<br />\n<br />\n要怪嘅係電池技術喇。<br />\n<br />\n無線耳機，啲聲唔拆就算。<br />\n<br />\n想靚聲嘅話，要隊埋個尿袋入個耳機度先得。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T00:52:09.000Z","msg":"你想話電池技術唔關apple事，<br />\n所以係非戰之罪？<br />\n<br />\n而家用戶體驗就係：<br />\n一大舊又貴又唔好聲既垃圾<br />\n<br />\n無線耳機d聲唔拆就算既話，<br />\n求其買個幾舊水既都得，<br />\n洗鬼幾千蚊買舊咁既野返黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你可以話無線耳機有極限，<br />\n唔可以同有線比，<br />\n但而家呢舊產品，<br />\n好明顯定位出錯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T01:01:09.000Z","msg":"定位出錯都係一樣好多fanboy撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T05:25:39.000Z","msg":"留意返<br />\nApple家下個定位就係幾十蚊貨仔賣幾千銀呃錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實定位冇出錯<br />\n只係佢地不願面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da4630bc33b21a